Lesson 47 课文讲解

    Do you like book?   X错
    Do you like a book? X错

    Do you like books?
    Do you like movies?
    Do you like stories？
    Do you like tea?
    Do you like English?

    black coffee    黑咖啡
    white coffee    白咖啡

